ote><br />\n手都有睇過下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72859bd9f45f1de2119d5c97912075a3c91c099d","tid":175751,"uid":95908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:53:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Chrome book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手都有睇過下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都有睇過下先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31170f5bb17ba6b92ead2571fcb7a40f0094b69","tid":175751,"uid":95908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>華碩 <br />\n個人用緊 覺得幾好用<br />\n經常要用3D software 畫野<br />\n都唔會話Lag</blockquote><br />\n巴打咩型號？</blockquote><br />\nVivoBook Pro N552VX <br />\n你可以睇下適唔適合你用</blockquote><br />\n巴打部野重唔重？"},{"pid":"9bf7474443471ea62dd4b722dadc63becb89b0c8","tid":175751,"uid":85527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T17:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>華碩 <br />\n個人用緊 覺得幾好用<br />\n經常要用3D software 畫野<br />\n都唔會話Lag</blockquote><br />\n巴打咩型號？</blockquote><br />\nVivoBook Pro N552VX <br />\n你可以睇下適唔適合你用</blockquote><br />\n唔該曬巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nASUS 個售後好仆街<br />\n你一壞就可以買過部新<br />\n<br />\n實例：我個部I7貴野，之前個screen壞左，去整時見佢報價2000，見買部新重貴過整，比錢走人。<br />\n點知佢老未，開頭話最遲都2個week內整好，點鳩佢整個screen用一個月。整撚完個screen,佢老母用9日壞鳩埋個hard drive 同keyboard。去問價時話我過撚左個保養期要比多300 total 2400。<br />\n我見咁貴走去出面d鋪問，個師博拆開部機個時問我係咪駁錯keyboard條線，我呆撚左，我完全唔識搞notebook,之後先醒起條華碩維修過,成件事唯一有疑點就係ASUS個maintenance.<br />\n利申：自問無粗用，用左2年個殼都無花<br />\nASUS香港代理維修係仆街。<br />\n<br />\n千奇唔好買！！！！<br />\n<br />\n你有成8000budget買部MacBook啦，起碼apple唔會伏鳩你。<br />\n順提Chromebook我有諗過下，但個人感覺唔好用，無謂用錢買垃圾"}]}